<b>ROOM OF AUTHORITY</b>

22:10.871 --> 22:14.581
<b>FIVE ELDERS
HIGHEST AUTHORITIES OF THE WORLD GOVERNMENT</b>

22:16.421 --> 22:20.021
<b>What did you come all the way here for?</b>

22:20.501 --> 22:22.331
