22:27.011 --> 22:29.371
<b>Since it's you, we made time.</b>

22:29.931 --> 22:32.531
<b>Yes... I appreciate that.</b>

22:33.221 --> 22:36.771
<b>Let's hear it.
Guys, would you excuse us?</b>

22:36.771 --> 22:37.681
<b>Yes, sir!</b>

22:56.351 --> 22:59.061
<b>I want to talk to you 
about a certain pirate...</b>

23:09.891 --> 23:13.761
